OL,6,FSome 3,000 people died as a result and
OL,7,Fsurvivors are living with lifelong
OL,8,Fhealth implications.
OL,10,FHe was taken to hospital aged 14 with
OL,11,Fa suspected ruptured appendix.
OL,13,FHe said there was no compassion or
OL,14,Fcare and he was made to feel like a
OL,15,Fleper with the door padlocked.
OL,17,FThat same year, Neil was told he had
OL,18,Fhepatitis B. Seven years later he was
OL,19,Fdiagnosed with hepatitis C, aged 21,
OL,20,Fand later, Aids.
