OL,6,FReport into compensation delays
OL,8,FSir Brian Langstaff today announced
OL,9,Fthat another report will look at the
OL,10,F"timeliness and adequacy" of the
OL,11,Fgovernment's response to compensation.
OL,13,FThe inquiry will also look at whether
OL,14,Ffurther hearings are required and if
OL,15,Fso, then this would mean reopening the
OL,16,Finquiry. This will be announced next
OL,17,Fmonth.
OL,19,F"When they die, their compensation
OL,20,Fdies with them"
