OL,3,C'It's been 42 years': Infected blood
OL,4,Cvictim still waiting for compensation
OL,6,FNeil told ITV News Central about the
OL,7,Fimpact of living with infected blood:
OL,8,F"It's been draining, it's been scary,
OL,9,Fmy parents have been called in three
OL,10,Ftimes because the doctors didn't think
OL,11,FI was going to survive the night, but
OL,12,FI am still here fighting."
OL,14,FHis wife Tina Walker said: "As the
OL,15,Fyears have gone on, more people from
OL,16,Fthe community are dying, when they
OL,17,Fdie, their compensation dies with them.
OL,19,F"I want everyone to be paid and to
OL,20,Fmove on.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
