OL,6,F"Walking is an issue, I am meant to be
OL,7,Fin a powered wheelchair all the time.
OL,8,FI can't do the things that I want to
OL,9,Fdo.
OL,11,F"I am becoming more dependent on Tina
OL,12,Fand everyone else around me."
