OL,3,C'It's been 42 years': Infected blood
OL,4,Cvictim still waiting for compensation
OL,6,FTina said she is frustrated with the
OL,7,Fcompensation process: "Nothing was
OL,8,Fdone at pace and done at all, even now
OL,9,Fwe have been registered with the
OL,10,Finquiry, we still have to provide more
OL,11,Fpaperwork for our claim.
OL,13,F"Everything has been slowed down, if
OL,14,Fanother government comes in, you go
OL,15,Fback ten steps."
OL,17,F"I am scared about being here in six
OL,18,For seven years' time"
