OL,3,C'It's been 42 years': Infected blood
OL,4,Cvictim still waiting for compensation
OL,6,FNeil said: "I want the government to
OL,7,Ftry and pay everyone by the end of
OL,8,Fthis year.
OL,10,F"I am scared about being here in six
OL,11,For seven years' time, I could get a
OL,12,Fchest infection or blood poisoning
OL,13,Fwhich I struggle to fight and then
OL,14,FTina gets nothing."
OL,16,F"This has been 42 years. My mum passed
OL,17,Faway in October, and now she has lost
OL,18,Fthe compensation she was owed.
OL,20,F"People are dying and it's not fair."
