OL,3,C'It's been 42 years': Infected blood
OL,4,Cvictim still waiting for compensation
OL,6,FAndy Evans, from Worcestershire was
OL,7,Finfected with HIV and Hepatitis C when
OL,8,Fhe was just five years old in 1983.
OL,10,FHe co-founded the Tainted Blood
OL,11,Fcampaign in 2006, which pushed for the
OL,12,Findependent inquiry - and that was
OL,13,Fpublished on 20 May last year.
OL,15,FAndy's parents were told by doctors
OL,16,Fthat he had HIV when he was 10, in
OL,17,F1987. But waited a few years before
OL,18,Ftelling him.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/13
