OL,3,C'It's been 42 years': Infected blood
OL,4,Cvictim still waiting for compensation
OL,6,FAt 13, Andy's mum took him on an
OL,7,Funexpected drive to the countryside to
OL,8,Ftell him he had HIV. It is likely he
OL,9,Fhad been infected at just five years
OL,10,Fold when he had Factor VIII injections
OL,11,Ffor haemophilia.
OL,13,FHe told ITV News Central: "People are
OL,14,Fanxious when the compensation will
OL,15,Farrive and if it will arrive in time.
OL,17,F"There was a huge amount of relief in
OL,18,Fthe community after the inquiry ended
OL,19,Fand proved that the scandal wasn't an
OL,20,Faccident.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/13
