OL,3,C'It's been 42 years': Infected blood
OL,4,Cvictim still waiting for compensation
OL,6,F"When we heard that the compensation
OL,7,Fscheme was announced, the community
OL,8,Fhadn't been consulted and it wasn't
OL,9,Fset out in a way which would meet the
OL,10,Fneeds of the people who had been
OL,11,Finfected or affected.
OL,13,F"The family members who have been
OL,14,Fimpacted through stigma and loss of
OL,15,Fwork have not been given adequate
OL,16,Fcompensation for what they went
OL,17,Fthrough.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/13
