OL,3,C'It's been 42 years': Infected blood
OL,4,Cvictim still waiting for compensation
OL,6,F"We are hoping that this new report
OL,7,Fwill make the government acknowledge
OL,8,Fthat it is failing in compensating
OL,9,Fpeople."
OL,11,FA Government spokesperson said: "The
OL,12,Fvictims of this scandal have suffered
OL,13,Funspeakably.
OL,15,F"We remain fully committed to
OL,16,Fcooperating with the inquiry and
OL,17,Facting on its recommendations, and are
OL,18,Fgrateful for its comprehensive work to
OL,19,Fdate.
